---
import site from '@/lib/site';
---

<section class="section s3-detail">
  <div class="container--narrow">

    <h2 class="s3-detail__heading">Reveal Unmatched Radiance</h2>

    <div class="s3-detail__card">

      <h3 class="s3-detail__card-subtitle">Signature Glass Facial</h3>

      <p class="s3-detail__best-for">
        Best for: Clients seeking to erase dullness, refine skin texture, and achieve a supreme, lasting radiance.
      </p>

      <p class="s3-detail__body">
        This revitalizing facial harnesses the power of Polydeoxyribonucleotide (PDRN) derived from salmon DNA to rejuvenate your skin at a cellular level. Experience a transformation to a smoother, more luminous complexion.
      </p>

      <ul class="s3-detail__list">
        <li class="s3-detail__list-item">
          <strong>Salmon DNA (PDRN):</strong> Stimulates collagen and elastin production, accelerates healing, and reduces inflammation for firmer, more youthful skin.
        </li>
        <li class="s3-detail__list-item">
          <strong>Deep Hydration Complex:</strong> Infuses the skin with essential moisture, plumping fine lines and restoring a dewy, radiant glow.
        </li>
        <li class="s3-detail__list-item">
          <strong>Gentle Exfoliants:</strong> Prepare the skin for optimal PDRN absorption by removing dull surface cells and improving texture.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <div class="s3-detail__cta">
        <a
          href={site.calcomUrl}
          class="btn btn--primary"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Schedule Now
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .s3-detail__heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h2);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-detail__card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background: var(--color-surface);
  }

  .s3-detail__card-subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    font-weight: var(--weight-regular);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .s3-detail__best-for {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .s3-detail__body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .s3-detail__list {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .s3-detail__list-item {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-left: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .s3-detail__list-item::before {
    content: '\2022';
    position: absolute;
    left: 6px;
    color: var(--color-cta);
  }

  .s3-detail__cta {
    margin-top: var(--space-xs);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .s3-detail__card {
      padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-sm);
    }
  }
</style>
